                    <p class="mb-3">
                        You are free to <strong>modify any assets, styles, and logic</strong> within the panel and
                        connector to suit your needs.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-3">
                        However, please be advised that <strong>removing or modifying the copyright notices in the
                            footer</strong> will result in the <strong>immediate and automatic termination of
                            support</strong> from the developer.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        Support is provided solely by Mihai209 to users who maintain the original branding in the
                        footer. By using this software, you agree to keep the copyright links visible.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer border-top border-secondary border-opacity-10">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary px-4 fw-bold" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
